# Windsurf Rules - Quick Reference

# Full docs: WINDSURF.md, AGENTS.md

## Project
DynamicCareerCanvas - Jekyll portfolio site

## Stack
Jekyll, Liquid, YAML, SCSS, Vanilla JS

## Core Rules

NO frameworks (React, Vue, jQuery)
Content in YAML (_data/)
Use CSS variables
Mobile-first responsive
Support light/dark modes
Test: bundle exec jekyll build

## File Structure
_data/ - YAML content
_includes/ - Templates
_layouts/ - Page layouts
_sass/ - Styles
assets/ - Static files

## Code Patterns

YAML:
company: "Name"
start_date: "YYYY-MM"

HTML/Liquid:
<div class="component-name">
  {{ include.data.field }}
</div>

SCSS:
.component {
  var(--spacing-md);

  @media (max-width: 768px) {}
}

JavaScript:
const fn = () => {};
// ES6+, no frameworks

## Windsurf Features
Flow Mode - Autonomous coding
Cascade - Multi-file edits
@workspace - Project queries
@file - File references

## Testing
bundle exec jekyll build
bundle exec jekyll serve --livereload

